snippet.title: A KNIGHT OF THE SEVEN KINGDOMS Official Episode 3 Trailer (2026) Game of Thrones
snippet.description:
Official A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms Episode 3 Trailer 2026 | More ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/App | Peter Claffey Series Trailer | HBO Max: 18 Jan 2026 | Details ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/show/2c5/a-knight-of-the-seven-kingdoms-the-hedge-knight-2026?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=description
A century before the events of "Game of Thrones", two unlikely heroes wandered Westeros… a young, naïve but courageous knight, Ser Duncan the Tall, and his diminutive squire, Egg. Set in an age when the Targaryen line still holds the Iron Throne and the memory of the last dragon has not yet passed from living memory, great destinies, powerful foes, and dangerous exploits all await these improbable and incomparable friends.

A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms (2026) is the new fantasy series by Owen Harris, starring Peter Claffey, Dexter Sol Ansell and Finn Bennett.
